msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Insturen"

#: accounts/templates/change-email-confirm.html
#: accounts/templates/password-reset-confirm.html
msgid "Invalid reset link"
msgstr "Ongeldige link voor opnieuw instellen"

#: accounts/templates/change-email.html
msgid ""
"An email has been sent to your new email address. Check it for instructions "
"on how to validate it."
msgstr ""
"Er is een e-mail verzonden naar uw nieuw e-mailadres. Raadpleeg hem voor "
"instructies over hoe het te valideren."

#: accounts/templates/email-change.html
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"Confirm your new email by visiting the following address\n"
"in your web-browser:"
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"Bevestig uw nieuwe e-mail door naar het volgende adres te gaan\n"
"in uw webbrowser:"

#: accounts/templates/email-change.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you didn't change your email on your account on %(site_name)s,\n"
"you can safely ignore this email."
msgstr ""
"Als u uw e-mail op uw account op %(site_name)s niet hebt gewijzigd, \n"
"kunt u deze e-mail gerust negeren."

#: accounts/templates/email-change.html
#: accounts/templates/email-password-creation.html
#: accounts/templates/email-password-reset.html
msgid "Thanks,"
msgstr "Bedankt,"

#: accounts/templates/email-password-creation.html
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"Please activate your account by visiting the following address\n"
"in your web-browser:"
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"Activeer uw account door in uw web-browser\n"
"naar het volgende adres te gaan:"

#: accounts/templates/email-password-creation.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you didn't create an account on %(site_name)s,\n"
"you can safely ignore this email."
msgstr ""
"Als u geen account heeft aangemaakt op %(site_name)s,\n"
"kunt u deze e-mail gerust negeren."

#: accounts/templates/email-password-reset.html
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"You can reset your password by clicking on the link below. If you did\n"
"not request a password reset, then you can ignore this."
msgstr ""
"Hallo,\n"
"\n"
"U kunt uw wachtwoord opnieuw instellen door op de onderstaande link te "
"kikken.\n"
"Indien u er niet om vroeg uw wachtwoord opnieuw in te stellen, kunt u dit "
"gerust negeren."

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Login"
msgstr "Aanmelden"

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Please login to continue"
msgstr "Gelieve in te loggen om verder te gaan"

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Your username and password didn't match. Please try again."
msgstr ""
"Uw gebruikersnaam en wachtwoord komen niet overeen. Probeer het opnieuw."

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid ""
"Your account doesn't have access to this page. To proceed, please login with "
"an account that has access."
msgstr ""
"Uw account heeft geen toegang tot deze pagina. Log in met een account dat "
"toegang heeft om verder te gaan."

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Please login to see this page."
msgstr "Gelieve in te loggen om deze pagina te zien."

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "E-mail:"
msgstr "E-mail:"

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Secure log-in:"
msgstr "Beveiligde login:"

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Switch to SSL"
msgstr "Overschakelen naar SSL"

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Did you lose your password?"
msgstr "Bent u uw wachtwoord kwijt?"

#: accounts/templates/login.html
msgid "Try resetting your password."
msgstr "Probeer uw wachtwoord opnieuw in te stellen."

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-complete.html
msgid "Okay! You have a new password"
msgstr "Oké! U heeft een nieuw wachtwoord"

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-complete.html
msgid "You can use your new password to"
msgstr "U kunt uw nieuw wachtwoord gebruiken om"

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-complete.html
msgid "log in"
msgstr "in te loggen"

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-confirm.html
msgid "Reset your password"
msgstr "Uw wachtwoord opnieuw instellen"

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-done.html
msgid "Password recovery in progress"
msgstr "Wachtwoordherstel in uitvoering"

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-done.html
msgid ""
"Okay! You should now get an email with a link. Click the\n"
"link."
msgstr ""
"Oké! U zou nu een e-mail met een link moeten ontvangen.\n"
"Klik op de link."

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-form.html
msgid "Password recovery"
msgstr "Wachtwoordherstel"

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-form.html
msgid "If you forgot your password, here is what we can do for you."
msgstr "Als u uw wachtwoord bent vergeten, is dit wat we voor u kunnen doen."

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-form.html
msgid "You should fill out this form."
msgstr "U moet dit formulier invullen."

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-form.html
msgid "You will get an email with a link. Click the link."
msgstr "U zult een e-mail krijgen met een link. Klik op de link."

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-form.html
msgid "Then the web app will allow you to change your password."
msgstr "Dan kunt u via de webapp uw wachtwoord wijzigen."

#: accounts/templates/password-reset-form.html
msgid "Not super hard. If you're ready, I'm ready."
msgstr "Niet supermoeilijk. Als u er klaar voor bent, ben ik er klaar voor."

